STAR WARS ATTRACT MODE TEXT DOCUMENTATION

	17-MAY-83

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BANNER PHASE

	"STAR WARS" logo stays in place near bottom of screen, brightness goes from off to normal brightness.
	Then it travels backwards, shrinking and dimming out as it goes. ( Typical "STAR WARS" effect )

	As the logo starts traveling backwards, the STORYLINE ( see below for text ) starts.  Each line is centered
	and a similar shrinking and dimming effect is used.  When all the text is visible the effect is stopped to
	allow reading ( about 20 seconds ).  Then one line at a time quickly recedes into the distance.

	STORYLINE text:
			 OBI WAN KENOBI IS GONE BUT HIS
			PRESENCE IS FELT WITHIN THE FORCE.
			THE EMPIRE'S DEATH STAR UNDER THE
			 COMMAND OF DARTH VADER NEARS THE
			 REBEL PLANET.  YOU MUST JOIN THE
			  REBELLION TO STOP THE EMPIRE.
			   THE FORCE WILL BE WITH YOU.
			            ALWAYS

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

FLIGHT INTRUCTION PHASE

	The text ( see below ) is output to the screen 1 line at a time and left there for about 20 seconds,
	then it fades out.

	Text:

	   FLIGHT INSTRUCTIONS TO RED FIVE
	 1.  YOUR X WING IS EQUIPPED WITH AN
	INVISIBLE DEFLECTOR SHIELD THAT
	WILL PROTECT YOU FOR x COLLISIONS.         ( Replace x with "6","7","8", or "9" depending on option switch settings )
	 2.  DEFLECTOR STRENGTH IS LOST WHEN
	A FIREBALL IMPACTS YOUR SHIELD OR
	WHEN YOU STRIKE A LASER TOWER OR
	TRENCH CATWALK.
	 3.  AIM YOUR LASERS WITH CURSOR TO
	EXPLODE  EMPIRE TIE FIGHTERS, LASER
	TOWER TOPS AND TRENCH TURRETS.
	 4.  SHOOT FIREBALLS BEFORE THEY
	IMPACT YOUR SHIELD.
	 5.  THE REBEL FORCE IS DEPENDING ON
	YOU TO STOP THE EMPIRE BY BLOWING
	UP THE DEATH STAR.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SCORING PAGE PHASE

	The text ( see below ) scrolls up from the bottom of the screen to its normal position,
	stays in place for about 20 seconds, then fades out.

	TEXT:

			 SCORING
	TIE FIGHTERS		     1,000
	DARTH'S SHIP		     2,000
	LASER BUNKERS		       200
	LASER TOWERS		       200
	TRENCH TURRETS		       100
	FIREBALLS		        33
	EXHAUST PORT		    25,000
	DESTROYING ALL TOWER TOPS   50,000	

